name: services
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool fiverr_pro_services.
Tool description: API to provide a list of vetted professional sellers for any category.
API description: Fetch a list of professional sellers for a specified service category from the Fiverr Pro Services API.

category_name.description: The name of the service category to fetch professional sellers for.

page.description: The page number of results to return. Default is 10.
